This is a word scramble made with plant-related words.
The scrambled words are parts of a plant or things a plant needs:
(flower, leaves, sunlight, water, seed, petals, roots, stem, fruit)

The user types in their answer and clicks 'check word.'
User receives alert if their answer is incorrect or correct.

*Needs score keeping.
*Needs conclusion for user to know they've cycled through all possible words.

Photos from Unsplash.
